		 <td><font face="Arial" size="+2">
		 Permanent Youth Secretariat to be established</font></a>
		 </td>
      </tr>
	  <tr><td><font face=arial>
        Persian daily<i> Hamshahri</i>, 3 Feb. 1998</font>
      </td></tr><font size=-1>
<tr><td><font face=arial size=2>
<p>A permanent secretariat is to be set up to co-ordinate the activities
of agencies dealing with youth issues.<br>
</p>

<p>Said Madani, executive director of the congress of youth issues in Iran
explained, &quot;The divergent approaches of these agencies had become very problematic
and their efforts were in need of co-ordination.&quot;<br>
</p>

<p>Mandani added that, &quot;There will also be a committee of youth
representatives to express their issues in their own words.&quot; <br>
<p>A permanent secretariat is to be set up to co-ordinate the activities
of agencies dealing with youth issues.<br>
</p>

<p>Said Madani, executive director of the congress of youth issues in Iran
explained, &quot;The divergent approaches of these agencies had become very problematic
and their efforts were in need of co-ordination.&quot;<br>
</p>

<p>Mandani added that, &quot;There will also be a committee of youth
representatives to express their issues in their own words.&quot; <br>
<p>A permanent secretariat is to be set up to co-ordinate the activities
of agencies dealing with youth issues.<br>
</p>

<p>Said Madani, executive director of the congress of youth issues in Iran
explained, &quot;The divergent approaches of these agencies had become very problematic
and their efforts were in need of co-ordination.&quot;<br>
</p>

<p>Mandani added that, &quot;There will also be a committee of youth
representatives to express their issues in their own words.&quot; <br>
<p>A permanent secretariat is to be set up to co-ordinate the activities
of agencies dealing with youth issues.<br>
</p>

<p>Said Madani, executive director of the congress of youth issues in Iran
